on the aid package.

298
00:17:52,571 --> 00:17:57,443
It'll be an especially large scandal if someone
from the embassy is involved.

299
00:17:57,443 --> 00:17:59,511
Mr. Saeba, how did you know?

300
00:17:59,511 --> 00:18:02,537
But I don't understand why
you're being targeted.

301
00:18:03,749 --> 00:18:06,479
Actually, I overheard them talking.

302
00:18:07,419 --> 00:18:10,422
I was working overtime late at night,

303
00:18:10,422 --> 00:18:13,225
